b3c39619-0ac4-4d0a-b32f-62d066acb5e0.message: When #people are free to do as they please, they usually #imitate each other.

b3c168e2-717f-4db6-8ad9-162a7148ce05.message: We are discreet #sheep; we wait to see how the drove is going, and then go with the drove.

b3f24676-c87c-4965-8d08-c41a54feca08.message: Blessed #is the man who, having nothing to say, abstains from giving us wordy evidence of the fact.
